{"by":"jpfaraco","id":47747415,"kids":[47747885,47752449],"parent":47741527,"text":"Finally being able to build something I&#x27;ve wanted for years: an alarm app that wakes me up 1 min earlier each day until I reach my wake time goal. Not sure if there is already anything like this out there, but I don&#x27;t really care. I&#x27;ve been learning a ton about native Android development and so far it&#x27;s been a painless process to be able to wake up earlier.","time":1776052653,"type":"comment"}